&lt;p&gt;Gummicube is a specialized division within Airship Group, Inc., focused exclusively on app discovery, App Store Optimization, mobile growth, and app store conversion. Gummicube helps brands grow high-quality mobile app audiences by improving visibility and conversion across the App Store and Google Play. Our work combines proprietary technology with hands-on strategy, analytics, creative testing, and client services. Gummicube serves apps of every size and category, including enterprise brands, high-growth startups, and new app launches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gummicube&#39;s culture is entrepreneurial, collaborative, client-focused, and hands-on. We value people who are curious about mobile growth, comfortable working across functions, and motivated by helping customers improve performance through data-driven recommendations and disciplined execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although Gummicube is part of Airship Group, this is a Gummicube-specific role. Candidates hired into this position will work with Gummicube&#39;s team, clients, services, and proprietary ASO technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gummicube.com&quot;&gt;www.gummicube.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Why Gummicube&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Gummicube, you will work in a focused, specialized business where app store performance, mobile growth, client outcomes, and data-driven execution are central to the work. Our teams are intentionally cross-functional, which means you often see how your work affects the full ASO process, including strategy, analytics, creative, client delivery, and product feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
